    "dbq_title": "inyandiko-Based ikibazo",
    "dbq_text": "inyandiko-Based ikibazo: umunyeshuri suzuma primary sources, build evidence-based arguments, and kora imyitozo the central ubumenyi of social-studies + ELA isuzuma. Generates inkomoko inyandiko, scaffolded ikibazo, and igisubizo keys aligned to your urwego.",
    "quiz_mode_title": "Pick the right igeragezwa uburyo",
    "quiz_mode_text": "Hitamo what iki igeragezwa is for. Exit Ticket checks today’s learning. Pre-Check probes prior knowledge before teaching and surfaces gaps as concept ikarita with a one-kanda \"Explain to ishuri\" AI broadcast. Formative Check is a byihuse mid-isomo pulse. Spaced Review tracks each umunyeshuri’s cross-igihe retention with a per-concept sparkline. Each uburyo tunes prompts, ikintu-type mix, and the live dashboard layout."
