    "escape_room_sequence_container": "Sequencing puzzle where you arrange ikintu chronologically, alphabetically, or logically. Kurura ikintu to reorder, or koresha arrow buto for keyboard navigation. ibirimo may be: historical events (chronological), inkuru elements (plot order), process intambwe (procedural), or size/quantity (numerical). Correct order unlocks the puzzle. Check your sequence before submitting—review for any obvious ikosa. Sequencing teaches: temporal reasoning, cause-effect relationships, and organizational thinking. Some puzzles have partially correct feedback (showing which ikintu are in right position). Work systematically from what you know most confidently. Team discussion helps verify ordering logic.",
